<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 20:08:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>据信在加沙被扣为人质的以色列人于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体在以色列坟墓中被发现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-believed-to-be-hostage-in-gaza-killed-on-oct-7-body-found-in-grave-in-israel/0000018f-3f71-d516-afbf-fff329b90000</link><description>哈马斯突然袭击以色列南部 210 天后，埃利亚基姆·利布曼 (Elyakim Libman) 的家人收到消息称他被谋杀，并没有像之前想象的那样被带到加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 19:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israeli-believed-to-be-hostage-in-gaza-killed-on-oct-7-body-found-in-grave-in-israel/0000018f-3f71-d516-afbf-fff329b90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长威胁摧毁巴勒斯坦权力机构是内塔尼亚胡最新的愚蠢举动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-threat-to-destroy-the-palestinian-authority-is-his-latest-asinine-antic/0000018f-3ea6-d414-a5bf-bfb7327e0000</link><description>以色列具体将如何做到这一点？一旦巴勒斯坦权力机构解散，谁将控制西岸？没有什么比以色列拒绝支持甚至拒绝接受乔·拜登的该地区计划更愚蠢的了</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:19:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-threat-to-destroy-the-palestinian-authority-is-his-latest-asinine-antic/0000018f-3ea6-d414-a5bf-bfb7327e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 210 天：据报道，以色列给哈马斯一周时间，以便在拉法行动之前达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-210-israel-reportedly-gives-hamas-week-to-make-deal-before-rafah-op/0000018f-3f49-d516-afbf-ffcb4b7b0000</link><description>英国宣布对四名以色列定居者实施制裁，该组织是极右翼组织，对约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人实施暴力行为。 ■ 据报道，以色列通知哈马斯，如果人质协议在一周内得不到落实，它将袭击拉法。加沙永久停火 ■ 战争进入 210 天后您需要了解以下内容</descrip